                <note rend="inline" type="source">123 P 54/585: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">William Phillips</persName>,
                        Personal Representative of President Roosevelt in India, to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Delhi</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-05T12:00:00+06:30"
                            >March 5, 1943—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received March 5—9:23 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>207. I am leaving today for Bombay and the south and shall return to Delhi about
                    April 1.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
